Title: <size=80>Duplicate Omniframes</size>
Content: Omniframes owned among options. Confirm and the duplicate ones will be <color=#0E70BD>converted</color> to <color=#0E70BD>Inver-Shards</color> of the corresponding amount. Continue?

Title: <size=80>Duplicate Coatings</size>
Content: The option includes Coatings you already own. If you confirm, the duplicate Coatings will be <color=#0E70BD>converted</color> into a certain number of <color=#0E70BD>Coating Blueprints</color>. Proceed?

Title: <size=80>アイコンが重複します</size>
Content: 選択のうち、所持済のアイコンは<color=#0E70BD>ナット</color>に<color=#0E70BD>変換</color>されます。続行しますか?
